D wind_cons_quant           Which quantity to conserve in wind
D wind_add_therm_e          Conserve energy when wind_cons_quant=momentum by
D &                         injecting the difference of wind luminosity
D &                         energy and kinetic wind energy as thermal energy?
PARAMETER wind_cons_quant   STRING "momentum" ["momentum", "energy"]
PARAMETER wind_add_therm_e  BOOLEAN FALSE


D wind_mass_load    Mass load the winds?
D wind_target_temp  Target wind injection temperature for mass loading.
D &                 Adjust wind velocity and mass to hit target temperature
D &                 T ~ 3/16 * mu / k_b * v**2 for a strong shock.
D &                 No effect if wind_mass_load=F
PARAMETER wind_mass_load        BOOLEAN FALSE
PARAMETER wind_target_temp      REAL    1e6

D wind_min_radius   Minimum wind injection radius
D wind_var_radius       Vary the radius by analytic calculation
D &                     of R1 from Weaver et al. 1977?
PARAMETER wind_min_radius       REAL    0.0
PARAMETER wind_var_radius       BOOLEAN     FALSE

D wind_perturb          Perturb the injected velocities from the wind?
D wind_perturb_stdev    What standard deviation would you like to perturb it by?
D &                     dimensionless stdev (gaussian normalized to mean 1)
PARAMETER wind_perturb  BOOLEAN  FALSE
PARAMETER wind_perturb_stdev    REAL     0.05
